  "title": "Motor Mechanic Technician",
  "description": "<p>Key Responsibilities:</p>\n<p>• Diagnose and repair motorcycles, including engine, transmission, and suspension systems</p>\n<p>• Perform routine maintenance tasks, such as oil changes and tire replacements</p>\n<p>• Provide accurate estimates for repair costs and timeframes</p>\n<p>• Communicate effectively with customers to understand their needs and concerns</p>\n<p>• Provide exceptional customer service and build lasting relationships with customers</p>\n<p>• Maintain a clean and organized work area</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p>• At least 3 years of experience working as a motorcycle mechanic</p>\n<p>• Ability to diagnose and troubleshoot complex mechanical problems</p>\n<p>• Ability to work in a fast-paced environment and handle multiple tasks simultaneously</p>\n<p>• Physical ability to lift and move heavy motorcycle parts and equipment</p>",
